<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-79-0610 </DOCNO><TEXT>Some experimental and theoretical aspects of charge symmetry breakingin the np system are reviewed. Possible experiments involving the np-andgt; d{pi}/sup 0/ reaction are described and the measurements at TRIUMFand IUCF of the neutron and proton analyzing powers in np elastic scatteringare discussed.</TEXT></DOC>